item.title: Prayer bpn13069 in Hiri Motu
item.description: Gwau: Dirava e, lauegu Dirava! Maoromaoro kara ena kwara gauna Oi atoa lauegu kwarana latanai bona hahegeregere kara ena herahera gauna Oi atoa lauegu vairana dekenai. Momokani Oi be henia gaudia bona harihari gaudia ibounai ena Biaguna. (Source category: MAOROMAORO KARA ENA GURIGURI) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13069)
